-- Quiet or Die module for Serenity. Standalone, like UE -- no shared runtime/theme table
-- to hook into, so this builds its own small panel matching the hub's look. Ported from
-- the old hub's QOD page: Auto Kill, Auto Farm (+ Safe Place, Mute Audio), Auto Revive,
-- Auto Event, Auto Reveal, and a live Coins/Wins readout. The old hub's ThemeObjects/
-- HubState wiring, keybind rebinding, and persistent execution-history panel were dropped
-- (this panel doesn't have that shared plumbing) -- toggles are plain click buttons.
